Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:03.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily, you saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.34,0:00:06.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am glad I was able to \Nprotect your homeland...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:10.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:12.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:23.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Black cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:28.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:04.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.84,0:02:06.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:13.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:16.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you are one of \Nthe Fallen. Just an Exceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:20.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've forgotten the debt you owe our king for \Nsaving you, and instead turn your blade against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:23.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the other Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:24.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Knightwalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:26.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:28.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:32.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:37.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Someone save Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:39.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't, Chagot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:43.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen, leave him to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:46.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scarlet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:48.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:50.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Knightwalker...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:51.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:59.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You intend to aim your spear at me, the \NPrince of Edolas, Erza Knightwalker?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:00.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:11.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince, you say? Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:15.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think of you as my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:17.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the voice of the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:19.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:25.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After 7 years of hiding in faraway lands, \Nyou have some nerve skulking back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:32.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you've been going around \NEarthland sealing off Anima!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:33.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've betrayed your country!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:36.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You sold out your own kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:38.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that voice coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:41.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like it's coming from \Ndeep inside the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:43.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:45.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:48.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Anima plan was a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:51.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Continuing to fight would \Nbe meaningless, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:55.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning? The meaning of fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:04:02.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that noise? Or wait, what is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:04.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The air is trembling from magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:11.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is retaliation against \Nthose who defy the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:14.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A one-sided extermination!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:19.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Some magical weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:29.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who stands in my way, \NI will eliminate them. Even you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:31.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be any trace left!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:33.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:36.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am no father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:40.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the King of Edolas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:47.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I'll wipe you out here,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.69,0:04:51.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and then no one will be left \Nto stop the Anima in Earthland!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:54.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll suck up another giant lacrima,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:57.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and then fuse it with the Exceed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:59.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it as many times as I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:00.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:09.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is impossible for the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:20.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The King's power is absolute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:28.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That shape... That magic power...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:30.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It can be none other!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:32.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My word...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:37.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Droma Anim!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Droma Anim?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:42.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It means "Dragon Knight" \Nin our native tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:45.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a hardened armored dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:47.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:51.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, it's in the shape of one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:53.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hardened armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.11,0:05:55.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Special anti-wizard lacrima...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:06:02.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wizard cancelers nullify all external magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:03.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a suit of armor you can pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:08.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The King's inside of it, \Ncontrolling Droma Anim!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:14.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My soldiers... Capture the Exceeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:15.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap... Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:26.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magicalize Cannon is fully charged!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:28.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Irradiate them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:39.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:41.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chagot... We should get farther away...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:43.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:45.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:47.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:53.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll protect the Exceeds \Nfrom the Royal Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:55.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Knightwalker's forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:56.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:07:01.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah... You don't get queasy \Nwhen riding this Legion...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:05.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have Troia cast on you \Nto help your motion sickness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:06.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:10.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This guy's like one of our buddies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:12.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop treating it like transportation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:13.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:15.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:18.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's been a long time \Nsince we did this bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:22.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough pointless banter for now. \NWhat'll we do about that giant thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:24.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call it pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:26.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless to even try and face it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:28.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic won't work on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:29.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:32.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Exceeds are defenseless now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:34.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't protect them, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:36.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:40.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect them while dodging me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:46.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let a single human escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:49.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll blast every last one of you to bits!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:53.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Begone!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:56.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystogan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:08:02.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystogan? Is that your \Nname on Earthland, Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:06.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, take this chance and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:07.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.12,0:08:10.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:11.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:14.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three Layered Magic Circle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's reflecting back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did that do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:27.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! So that's Mystogan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:32.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:34.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't even scratch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:36.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:37.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:42.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly! This is the \Npower of Wizard Canceler!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:48.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what wizard faces it, \Nno magic will work on Droma Anim!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:57.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystogan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.86,0:09:02.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're much more suited to \Ncrawling along the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:06.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should wander along the ground \Nuntil you give up and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:11.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... Ice Make...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:16.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:18.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm gonna be sick, \Nand I'm not even Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:20.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Monmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:25.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, how beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:29.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn every Exceed into \Na lacrima. Spare no one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:33.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare the humans hide the \Nfact they had such a monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:38.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The beast that darkens the \Nheavens, leading to extinction...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:43.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Its name is the Dragon Knight, Droma Anim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:51.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Long, long ago, not only Edolas, but Extalia \Nas well came very close to being wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:57.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so dangerous, the humans \Nshould have sealed it themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:01.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you mean, almost wiped out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:04.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:07.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the legend,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:11.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,when the Droma Anim dyed the heavens black,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:15.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the world lost more than \Nhalf of its magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:21.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! There's no way we \Ncan fight while dodging that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:23.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Legipyon, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:28.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should use Lucy as a decoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:29.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You little devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:30.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:33.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop breaking the flow of conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:47.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who? Magic shouldn't work on Droma \NAnim, so who is attacking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:50.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Sky Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:55.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:11:00.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, not bad, Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.29,0:11:04.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... The attacks from the \Ntwo of you did more damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:07.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it... How dare \Nthey do that to my cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:11.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! It's {\i1}you{\i0} fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:13.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:13.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:15.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:19.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on. Protect the cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:23.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:27.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But will just the three of them \Nbe okay against that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:29.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:35.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're up against a dragon. They're \Nthe only ones who can defeat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:38.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The dragon-hunting wizards...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:41.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Slayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:59.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are lacrima?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:01.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's turned into a lacrima?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:03.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dragon Chain has been severed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:07.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and with it was lost a lacrima that could have \Nbeen 10 years of magic power for this kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:13.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if all the Exceed are magicalized, \Nthat won't change the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:19.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He even brought out Droma Anim... \NHow is this even going to end?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:21.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You really shouldn't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily, you're safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:28.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:33.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey... Look at those humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:36.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the three of them plan on fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:37.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:40.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But kind of cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:42.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chagot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:45.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us escape to somewhere \Na bit farther away...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:47.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we stay here, we'll get caught up in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:52.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Salamander.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:54.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Teaming up with you, {\i1}again{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:56.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I can settle things
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.89,0:13:00.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,after we give this thing \Nthe bustin' up it deserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:02.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:05.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Foolish children!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:07.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll provide support!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:10.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,O swift wind that dashes through the heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:15.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:18.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My body... It's light as a feather!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:20.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vernier!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:27.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They dodged?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:30.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:34.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't set the aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:36.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Fist of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pillar of the Iron Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:47.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic shouldn't work at all on Droma Anim!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:51.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's taking damage... Just a tiny bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:56.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn this thing! How hard is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're barely denting it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.01,0:13:59.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:02.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,O strength of arm to cleave the heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:09.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:14.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Power is welling up inside of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:16.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's magic that increases your attack power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:18.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.03,0:14:24.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Their magic power is increasing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.57,0:14:29.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dazzling Blaze of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:31.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Spears of the Iron Dragon! Demon Poles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:35.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.71,0:14:37.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:40.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Launch the Dragon Knight Balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.06,0:14:46.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:49.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vernier!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:56.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're homing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:15.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:17.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:19.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more where that came from!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:23.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't gonna let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:26.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:31.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still 2 left!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:34.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are... Don't, Natsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:36.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're different than the ones from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:53.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You naive, foolish wizards!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:56.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourself dragon hunters?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:15:59.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:03.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's {\i1}eating{\i0} the Dragon \NKnight Ball's explosion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:11.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And {\i1}he's{\i0} eating my tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:17.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this awful fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:20.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't never tasted anything \Nthat pissed me off more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:26.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That ain't it. But in the meantime...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:30.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've eaten, I'm all revved up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:32.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:34.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one real annoying pest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:37.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:41.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These are Earthland wizards...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:45.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is strong. It ain't called \Na "dragon" for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:49.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break. This ain't \Neven close to a dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:53.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he's the king of this land, \Nhe doesn't have a single bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:55.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got incredible self-confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:16:59.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:03.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These are Dragon Slayers...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:10.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, all the more for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:12.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.79,0:17:16.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's collecting magic power from the air?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:19.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's flowing into that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:27.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they're here,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:30.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can put my Anima plan \Ninto motion once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:38.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For a future of eternal magic \Npower, I will capture these three.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:42.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... They are already dangerous weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:47.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No imprisonment... I'll have to break \Nthem into a couple of pieces each.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:53.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I will rid everyone \Nof the will to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:58.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With the Black Heavens power Droma Anim has!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:08.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:20.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did a mosquito just try and bite me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:25.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:28.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with the power of Arms, \Nour attacks won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:34.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you feel this overwhelmingly \Npowerful magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:38.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is incredible! Don't kneel before \Nme! Don't plead for your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:43.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to just keep standing \Nthere shaking like leaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:50.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be afraid, Dragon Wizards!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:04.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:05.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:07.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:10.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You let yourself be done \Nin on purpose before?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:16.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:18.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How are your injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:20.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This? It's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:24.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't! You're just barely able to stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:28.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to leave Droma \NAnim up to Natsu and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:31.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have something we must do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:32.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:35.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My final work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:39.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For that, I'll need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:48.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:49.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear screams all the way over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:51.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They caught up to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:52.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Royal Army has...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:54.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And in so many numbers...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:56.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:57.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:20:01.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't, then the Exceed are finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:03.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fight, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:07.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We'll protect our homeland!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:10.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you, Scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:19.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, it was a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:20.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An ambush?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:22.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dodge, Legipyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:36.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Legipyon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:40.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:43.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:46.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who turn against the King \Ncannot be allowed to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.92,0:20:49.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will finish you for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:50.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting off onto the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:57.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding the both of you up is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:21:00.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Legipyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:03.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Carla! And \Nwould you stop squirming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.15,0:21:06.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:08.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though there's only one of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:13.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, now I'm wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:14.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.02,0:21:26.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scarlet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:29.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's time we finished \Nthis, Knightwalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:35.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, dismount to the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.89,0:21:39.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight her myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:39.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:46.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The old capital of those filthy cats?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:49.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A fitting place to make your grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:52.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I say the same back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:58.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even as you are Erza, you have \Nhurt Fairy Tail far too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:04.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even as you are Erza, you \Nhave turned against our King.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:08.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for two Erzas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.45,0:22:21.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This fight continues until \Nonly one of us remains!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.35,0:23:59.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, what does it mean to be alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.52,0:24:01.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this all of a sudden, Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.30,0:24:02.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you eat something funky?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.64,0:24:04.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just like always!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.42,0:24:06.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what's your answer, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.35,0:24:07.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's simple, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.90,0:24:10.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Living is eatin', sleepin' \Nand gettin' into fights!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.62,0:24:14.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're actually quite the philosopher, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.34,0:24:16.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Those Who Are Alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.97,0:24:18.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's your answer, Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.85,0:24:22.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Catching fish, cooking fish, \Nand eating fish, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.87,0:24:25.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much the same things...
